# README Formatting Style

## Headers

- Use `#` for the document title only (e.g., `# README '/folder/name'` or project title)
- Use `##` for main sections (e.g., `## Table of Contents`, `## Activities`)
- Use `###` for subsections when needed
- Limit to two heading levels for clarity
- Keep headings concise and descriptive
- Section headers may include emojis (see below)

